Reasoning: The paper discusses the design and optimization of hopping robots for exploration of extreme environments on the Moon and Mars. This involves multidisciplinary design and control optimization, which falls under the scope of robotics (cs.RO). The use of automated techniques for design optimization also suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the need for mission assurance and operations culture, which falls under the scope of systems engineering (cs.SY) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper specifically mentions the design of SphereX robots, which suggests a focus on robotics and robots (cs.ROBOTS).
